{
  "stem": "13258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went with that unit from Sielce on the Oka, first, through the area of Smolensk, where we became like a third row of defense.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From there, we moved to the Ukraine in the area of-- between two Jewish towns, [INAUDIBLE] and [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Berdychiv, ?] in a little village at the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From there, we went to a place in the Ukraine near the city of Luck-- L-U-C-K-- in an area full of anti-Soviet guerrillas, where we had to watch ourselves terribly.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lost-- our regiment subsequently lost a truck with its crew over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We never recovered either the crew nor the truck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from there, in June of-- beginning of July, 1944 we went into action.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My regiment was an under-20-millimeter-mortar regiment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's an-- our artillery was an artillery shell, weighing 16 pounds, with a reach of 6 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We fired 38,000 rounds of ammunition during the period when I served with them, and I kept the statistics, so I know what we did.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wrote the history of the regiment after the war for the army, for the Ministry of Defense in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we participated in the fights from the river [INAUDIBLE] to the Vistula, to the right bank of the Vistula in Warsaw and the left bank of Vistula, in January of 1945, to [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Pomerania, ?] the Baltic Sea at Kolberg, across the [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Oda ?] River, participated in the surrounding of Berlin, never got into Berlin proper while we were fighting, and to the [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Elbe ?] River, where we were when the war-- No.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Where we were-- three days and then we were withdrawn to a place near Berlin called [INAUDIBLE] where we were when-- on May 8th, when the war came to an end.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
